@NODE 6.1. "Master page bug"

There is a bug in master page's also!!!  It assumes every new section begins
with  left  master  page.   But  this  is  not  correct!  If you have ended
previous  chapter on left page, then next section must begin with the right
master page, but it doesn't!!!

NEW! Ok, this is maybe not a bug but an undocumented feature :-)

@ENDNODE

